description:
THE PERSONALITY AND CAREER of the world's most charismatic superspy has held millions of fans spellbound for decades. Now, thanks to M, head of MI6, the Bond Mission files have been thrown open for the first time to reveal a wealth of dazzling "top secret" information, including:

- Details of all major characters and events from 007's thrill-packed assignments;
- Spectacular illustrations of the lairs, plans, and superweapon belonging to all the major Bond villains;
- Never-before-seen illustrations and photographs that explain how Q Branch's ingenious gadgets and vehicles really worked;
- Blow-by-blow accounts of Bond's most death-defying chases and battles.

